Installing Buxon
****************

Short Answer:
-------------

	make install


Long Answer:
------------

Dependencies:

	- swaml >= 0.0.6
	- python >= 2.4.0
	- rdflib >= 2.4.0
	- gtk+ >= 2.6.0
	- pygtk >= 2.6.0
	- gazpacho >= 0.6.6
        
As root user you may run:

	make install
	
This command will install Buxon at common directories. Then it'll be available
a new command: 'buxon'.

To uninstall it's also easy:

	make uninstall

